{"tid":2222943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"野豬一家 5 口到中銀總行嬉水玩「滑梯」 網民：很可愛","createTime":"2020-09-29T12:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T13:48:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2c91b301e860aac81350083a798ef63598bc8ef1","tid":2222943,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2763002/%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%205%20%E5%8F%A3%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E7%B8%BD%E8%A1%8C%E5%AC%89%E6%B0%B4%E7%8E%A9%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%91%E6%A2%AF%E3%80%8D%20%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2763002%2F%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25205%2520%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%258A%2580%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25AC%2589%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%258E%25A9%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25BB%2591%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E3%2580%258D%2520%2520%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2584%259B&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=34f8b929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2763002/%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%205%20%E5%8F%A3%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E7%B8%BD%E8%A1%8C%E5%AC%89%E6%B0%B4%E7%8E%A9%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%91%E6%A2%AF%E3%80%8D%20%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B</a></span><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n野豬一家 5 口到中銀總行嬉水玩「滑梯」 網民：很可愛<br />\n<br />\n | 梁綺文 | 25-09-2020 19:03 |   | <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2763002/zhu0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2763002%2Fzhu0_1024.jpg&h=835abf16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野豬走入社區的事件常有發生。近日，網上就瘋傳了兩條野豬一家到中環嬉戲，甚至是嬉水的片段。不少網民看過後都大呼可愛，見野豬仔摔了一跤亦不禁為牠感到擔心！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上瘋傳野豬一家 5 口出現在中環嬉戲甚至是戲水的片段<br />\n<br />\n只見大野豬就帶著 4 隻小野豬落水暢泳，一隻小野豬更不小心摔跤變成玩滑梯<br />\n<br />\n漁護署呼籲市民切勿接觸野豬<br />\n<br />\n【相關報道】野豬都識過馬路？一大三小沿行人輔助線走【下一頁】<br />\n<br />\n從網傳的片段及照片可見，一隻成年野豬帶著 4 隻小野豬在中環中國銀行總行附近出沒。只見牠們對總行對出的花園水池十分有興趣，很快，大野豬就帶著 4 隻小野豬落水暢泳，似乎十分開心。在其中一條片段中，一隻小野豬似乎在樓梯旁斜坡摔了一跤，無法穩住身軀結果就像玩滑梯一般向下滑去，不少人見到後都擔憂小野豬會受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據香港漁護署指出，野豬一般習慣躲避人類，僅在受挑釁或受驚嚇時可能會作出攻擊行為 ，尤其是有領導地位的雄豬或是帶著小豬的母豬。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2763002/zhu1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2763002%2Fzhu1_600.jpg&h=3e635c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上瘋傳野豬一家 5 口出現在中環嬉戲甚至是戲水的片段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2763002/zhu2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2763002%2Fzhu2_600.jpg&h=49fd8ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只見大野豬就帶著 4 隻小野豬落水暢泳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2763002/zhu3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2763002%2Fzhu3_600.jpg&h=d258c2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一隻小野豬更不小心摔跤變成玩滑梯。"},{"pid":"886bbcde4f121445c4f293114fc87505b79a7dd3","tid":2222943,"uid":158899,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"係中國 中銀 佢成家已經變左乳豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdc2acce28548d64088eab3fd7bdb556cf167ec","tid":2222943,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"黃偉民易經講堂 <br />\n露天機 野豬從天降中銀 時辰到 大陸經濟響喪鐘 <br />\n分清楚 使用權和擁有權<br />\nSep 29, 2020<br />\n<br /