/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797909aaf4e504338435d8623221112f75f7ae53","tid":2222943,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"中環有野豬<br />\n又見大量老鼠<br />\n咩事"},{"pid":"035dc8216afe73217a89a518796c35fb22167d05","tid":2222943,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"D狗又唔做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2653262a909499c12415e3598745ce2c54e7e998","tid":2222943,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e1f28e37bfa53a428074c172304faab392c80d","tid":2222943,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200928/WKY24ZBVZNEUHBLAWHPWGCJY4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200928%2FWKY24ZBVZNEUHBLAWHPWGCJY4I%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=fa9439b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200928%2FWKY24ZBVZNEUHBLAWHPWGCJY4I%2F&h=512d569c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200928/WKY24ZBVZNEUHBLAWHPWGCJY4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n五豬闖中銀 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z4yAcTyhXQhZ7A28T3DBcaPJrIg=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2IWP7ZHVSBELXMXXSOKVQ36KRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz4yAcTyhXQhZ7A28T3DBcaPJrIg%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2IWP7ZHVSBELXMXXSOKVQ36KRY.jpg&h=02ba681b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走過中環中國銀行總行旁邊的水池，不禁多看了兩眼，因為前一天有一家大小五隻野豬，也不知從何而來，竟跳進這個假山石堆成的水池裏暢泳，五隻野豬歡快的泳姿被人拍片上網，一下子國際知名。所以翌日我經過那裏，特地張望一下，畢竟是罕見的奇景，妄想也能見一見。<br />\n<br />\n古有五鼠鬧京華，今有五豬闖中銀，當天有朋友在網上問：在滙豐雞毛鴨血之際，旁邊的中銀有野豬暢泳贈興，是什麼兆頭。我說你真把我當神棍了，誰知道這是什麼兆頭！我唯一關心的，是這家野豬的行走路綫，若是家住山頂樹林之中，沿山頂道，馬己仙峽道、花園道走到山腳中銀，一路蹓躂，身旁車水馬龍，野豬們優游自在，拖兒帶女，真是一道有趣風景。只是在中銀水池暢泳完畢，不知找不找得到路回家。<br />\n<br />\n自從疫情爆發，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"258ef6315a05eac15cc61d7dabfb2e3fc3c935bf","tid":2222943,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2653262a909499c12415e3598745ce2c54e7e998","tid":2222943,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7004f5bc99e2ee3092293277c9e5efc3f8dcdf4","tid":2222943,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"野豬BB🐗😍"},{"pid":"98b6abe639b7076b2b92ece3d30b06e4e8fe378e","tid":2222943,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035dc8216afe73217a89a518796c35fb22167d05","tid":2222943,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"D狗又唔做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"對野豬仲溫柔過對付示威者."},{"pid":"c9ee57298321d90a21984578dcbc6f02e1ed62cb","tid":2222943,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">是靚Post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如誠實啲講，我覺得其他戰線好悶，我唔做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222667</a><br />\n<br />\n絕望了.....贏不了.....只係你嘅幻想<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222502</a><br />\n<br />\n月餅切成12份許願法！？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gfageS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gfageS</a><br />\n<br />\n上過熱門<br />\n<br />\n十二港人無人提？咁咪我開囉，但無人推呢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222381</a>"},{"pid":"0df58a3ed2fc6743088a82b01378e2af0d17b1d2","tid":2222943,"uid":187647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"5G入水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}